                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <h3>The objective of Minesweeper is to expose all open areas on the board without hitting any
                        bombs/mines.</h3>
    
                    <ol>
                        <li>Left click on any available space on the grid. If it is a bomb, you already lose!</li>
                        <li>The numbers on the board represent how many bombs are adjacent to a square. For example, if a
                            square has a "3" on it, then there are 3 bombs next to that square. The bombs could be above,
                            below, right left, or diagonal to the square.</li>
                        <li>Avoid all bombs and expose all empty spaces, and win the game!!</li>
                        </ol>
                </div>
            </div>
                    
